<item>
            <title>[LU-19563] Increase default lnet_interfaces_max to 512</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19563</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need to increase default lnet_interfaces_max to 512.&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
we are running into conditions where 126 is not enough especially when there are lots of vlans.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
